Key Match Events: Adam Zampa took three wickets for 21 runs
Joe Root was dismissed for 13 runs due to a review
Post-Match Reflections: England have lost six of their seven games in India
Australia have leapfrogged New Zealand to move to third in the table
Miscellaneous Highlights: Jonny Bairstow scored a first-ball duck
Others: England's remaining two games still come with the incentive of finishing in the top eight and securing qualification for the 2025 Champions Trophy
The match was played in soupy Ahmedabad
